      <section id="id4793123">
        <title>ACTIVITY 2: To collect information on nutritional value in foodstuffs [LO 1.2] </title>
        <para id="id11600072">Collect some wrappers or packaging from foodstuffs. Study the information provided on these:</para>
        <para id="id18132173">1. What is the unit of measurement for energy? ______________________________</para>
        <para id="id15898966">2. How many of these units should you take in daily? _________________________</para>
        <para id="id3203431">3. Try to explain why someone who is on a hunger strike should not be selected to take part in a marathon.</para>
        <para id="id16889589">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
